body.name: PZOZ 6 Pack Cord Organizer, Adhesive Charger Cable Clips, Wire Holder Keeper Organizer, Charging USB Cable Management for Home Office Desk Phone Car Wall Desktop Nightstand (Black)
features: 【Clip Design】Perfectly organizer varous sizes of wires. The desk cord holder clip can be applied to iPhone charger cables, USB cords, HDMI thick cables, computer power cords, ect. Diameter of cable is <7mm (0.27 inch).

【No-Residue Adhesive】This cable organizer comes with a strong adhesive tape that can tightly adhere to any clean smooth surfaces. Adhered easily to desk, glass, metal, ceramic tile and other smooth surfaces. Clear the removable stickers will not damage surfaces. 【TIPS】When Sticking, keep pressing for 1-2 minutes to enhance the adhesion of the sticky pad. Please wait 12-24 hours before using.

【Excellent Material & Easy To Use】Using high-quality PC material, durable. The matte surface treatment process, more delicate and beautiful.Tear off the sticker on the back and stick it where you need it. Then open the clip and put in different size cords, press to close clamp. Allows cords to stretch back and forth for easy placement and access.

【Make Your Life Easier】Using this cable clips holder to tidy up your cluttered cords, make your numerous cables nicer, organized, and safer. 6 Pcak clips allows you to use in more places. Like desktop, tableside, table corner, office, wall or inside the car.
【Service】PZOZ offers 12-month quality service. Package includes: 6 x Cord Organizer.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars We've got a winner
reviews.reviewText: I've used a lot of wire management gizmos over the years and this style is by far my favorite. It's the only one that's never failed and I no longer find myself fishing for fallen cables behind my desk or nightstand.Note that these fit your usual USB cables like those that come with a cell phone. I tried to put an HDMI cable in one and it didn't fit because the wire was too thick.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little things
reviews.reviewText: Adhesive is very strong and doesn't come off accidentally yet comes off clean if you really try. Most cables get bound up and don't smoothly slide down but if you use braided cables it'll usually work as advertised. If the hole was a little larger or the edge was more rounded they may work better but overall I'm satisfied with the purchase and would recommend them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great Idea, needs refinement
reviews.reviewText: I loved the idea of these clips. How many of us have cords at our night stands, coming up from behind our desk, kitchen counters, etc. They hold the cords from dropping down behind what they are laying on. I found them easy to use, easy to open and held the cord in place. One drawback. The adhesion needs to be stronger. Some cords are heavy and have some weight. These clips are having trouble with that, and if you open and close them a bunch it pyres them off. Have heavy duty double sticky tape ready to replace. That's why I gave them 4 stars. Great idea, better adhesion is recommended.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023

reviews.reviewText: Everything about it so far is very good, lets me organize my charging cables on the edge of my work desk. The adhesive on them is very interesting, it’s almost like a gel pad. Fit and finish is great, no plastic burrs, no misaligned tabs

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Work great and fit various cord sizes
reviews.reviewText: These are fantastic and are worth it. The plastic on the underside to reveal sticky part is a little hard to get off, but I would still choose these knowing that. I have two at work and two at home. They got my typical charging cord for my computer as well as my HDMI cord for my external monitor. They show no signs of coming off and it has been about 2 months since I ordered.
